- Task #1204 (P4): ICMT synthetic lethality addendum — COMPLETED. ICMT not confirmed as significant hit in DepMap. No cohort reaches FDR<0.05. Four cohorts show expected SL direction (Bowel d=-0.70 n=8, Lymphoid d=-0.48 n=13, Breast d=-0.38 n=10, Ovary d=-0.30 n=6) but all severely underpowered. Five cohorts show opposite direction. Cysmethynil not in PRISM 24Q2. Phase 3 found ZERO PTEN-selective dependencies genome-wide across all cancer types — general underpowering issue. Verdict: literature-supported target, uninformative null result due to power constraints. No drug-candidate/high-priority flag. Non-blocking addendum. Journaled as #1929.
